#   INK: all 11 NPC story files compiled — npc_sarah, npc_patrol_nurse, npc_ravi, npc_david,
#        npc_helen, npc_hartley, npc_sharma, npc_bed4_patient, npc_bed2_patient,
#        npc_chair_patient, npc_pharmacist; see inline comments on each NPC for knot list
#   ITEM: ravi_rfid_card — added to Ravi's itemsHeld; given to player in npc_ravi.ink:start
#
# GLOBAL VARIABLES — wiring status
#   [WIRED via minigames]
#   itsec_authorised          — dual_auth minigame (MG-11) on correct IT Security PIN ✓
#   clinical_eng_authorised   — dual_auth minigame (MG-11) on correct Clinical Eng PIN ✓
#   dual_auth_failed          — dual_auth minigame (MG-11) on 5-min timeout ✓
#   backup_recovery_source    — backup-recovery minigame (MG-07) on source confirm ✓
#   recovery_eta_hours        — backup-recovery minigame (18 for cloud, 0 for NAS/tape) ✓
#   backup_restore_initiated  — backup-recovery minigame (MG-07) on confirm ✓
#   pump_dose_correct         — infusion_pump minigame (MG-08) ✓
#   pump_dose_error           — infusion_pump minigame (MG-08) ✓
#   [WIRED via compiled Ink]
#   briefing_played           — npc_sarah.ink:arrival_briefing (setGlobalOnStart) ✓
#   bed4_escalated            — npc_sarah.ink:escalate_bed4 ✓
#   safety_claim_hc001_assessed — npc_david.ink:safety_case_hc001 ✓
#   safety_claim_hc003_assessed — npc_david.ink:safety_case_hc003 ✓
#   safety_claim_hc007_assessed — npc_helen.ink:safety_case_hc007 ✓
