#   [WIRED via scenario timers / eventMappings]
#   patient_bed4_state        — timers escalate → distressed → critical → deceased ✓
#   patient_bed2_state        — pump_dose_error eventMapping → sedated ✓
#   debrief_started           — verify_drug_library task onComplete ✓
#   ico_deadline_missed       — 45-min timer if ico_notified still false ✓
#   [NOT YET WIRED — genuine gaps]
#   isolation_aborted         — no setter; needs MG-11 cancel/timeout branch
#   patient_bed2_deceased     — read in timer conditions but never set; needs MG-08 double-jeopardy or Ink
